channel.title: Want your server big?
channel.description:
I have placed this in the Help section due to people getting help with getting their server big. Please read the following.
I am a Youtube Mass Marketer which I have 3 years experience with Youtube Marketing. After helping out a few other servers get their servers off to a good start I am looking to help out (1) more server in the meantime.
How Can I Help? I will be uploading anywhere from 5k+ Youtube Videos Weekly with the best of the best programs and programs I have made as well. My crew which is small atm is dedicated to get your server players and a good community.
Want us to help you? Pm me on here or Skype me austin.rohrer (Target). We prefer to play 317's but we are willing to play others and help others out.
Currently: Looking for another server to help and play on. Currently helping: Was Pkhonor did 1,700 videos for them. Rewards gotten so far: In game rewards such as high valued items.
Thanks guys for reading hope we can help you ASAP! Questions please post below and I will try to answer them to the best of my ability.
Please POST before skyping me with the form below...
Server Name: Link to server forums: Link to server Client/download: Number of players at the moment: Why should we help you and your server: Kind of server: How long has it been up: Any Downtime: VPS: Are you an experience Coder:
We would love to play a game with constant updates and such. Thanks for reading hope we can help!
